{
  "id": "adv_event_2204_01_04",
  "title": "愛歌う星の継承者 4話 禁断の恋",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、私はどうすれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ what should I do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もし……仮に私が、彼を受け入れたとしたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If… hypothetically‚ I accept him…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、もっと先の段階を求められて……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Surely‚ he would be expect a further thing…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "きゃー！　きゃー！！　そんなの恥ずかし過ぎますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaa! Kyaa!! That's too embarrassing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、ちょっとくらいなら……ってバカあああ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But‚ if it's just a little bit… no‚ stupid!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すず、どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ what's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 866.6666667000022
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 400.00000000000216
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "クッションなんか抱きしめて騒いで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hugging a cushion and making a fuss…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "例の企画のレッスン、うまくいってないのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is the lesson for the special project not going well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "レレレレッスンどころじゃありませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not a le-le-le-lesson at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今、私は人生で最大の選択を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ I'm facing the biggest decision in my life!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "突き付けられているのですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's being thrust upon me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "――は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ああっ、{user}さんたら、こんなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "公私混同ですのに……はぁ、もう困りましたわぁ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He shouldn't mix personal and professional matters… Haa‚ I'm so troubled…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、すずが一人で悶えてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ Suzu is in distress on her own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "何がどうしたのよ？　ちゃんと説明しなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong? Explain properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "相談に乗ってあげるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll listen and offer advice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "えっ？　ですが、これはプライベートなことですし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? But‚ this is a private matter…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "第一、口にするのは恥ずかしい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ it's embarrassing to say it out loud…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "今のままの方が恥ずかしいと思うけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it's more embarrassing to keep it to yourself like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、一人でくねくね悶えるのはやめなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ stop squirming on your own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なっ……！　私は悶えてなんかいませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha…! I'm not squirming!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも{user}さんが……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First of all‚ {user}-san…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが、何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ what about him?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "あっ……！　いえ、別に、その、なんでも――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…! No‚ it's nothing‚ well‚ um… anything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "彼が原因なのね。話しなさい、すず",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He's the cause‚ isn't he? Tell us‚ Suzu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "話すまで部屋に帰さないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You won't go back to your room until you talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ううっ、莉央さん、肩！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uu‚ Rio-san‚ my shoulder!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "私の肩を掴む握力が尋常じゃありませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your grip on my shoulder is abnormal!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すず、莉央さんは素手でくるみを割れるらしいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ Rio-san can crack walnuts with her bare hands.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "早く話した方がいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's better to talk quickly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "脅しはやめて下さい！　分かりましたわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please stop threatening me! I understand!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "話しますわよ！　だから放して下さいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll talk! So please let go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい、放したわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ I let go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_04-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、話して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ speak.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "実は、{user}さんに……告白されましたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ {user}-san… confessed to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
